At least one person died and 10 others were critically injured in two separate road accidents in the Eastern Cape yesterday. Near Sterkspruit one passenger was declared dead on the scene and seven people were critically injured when two vehicles collided head-on in the early hours.For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions.&nbsp;